|5 |        └─MERGE GROUP BY                        |           |5       |186         |
|6 |          └─SORT                                |           |5       |184         |
|7 |            └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                  |           |5       |181         |
|8 |              ├─HASH JOIN                       |           |6       |99          |
|9 |              │ ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN              |           |6       |92          |
|10|              │ │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN             |ITEM       |5       |14          |
|11|              │ │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|STORE_SALES|2       |16          |
|12|              │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN               |STORE      |12      |3           |
|13|              └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET           |DATE_DIM   |1       |16          |
=======================================================================================
