|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE          |                |100     |1344        |
|2 |  └─LIMIT                      |                |100     |1254        |
|3 |    └─MERGE GROUP BY           |                |100     |1254        |
|4 |      └─SORT                   |                |103     |1242        |
|5 |        └─HASH JOIN            |                |196     |1164        |
|6 |          ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |DATE_DIM        |88      |51          |
|7 |          └─HASH JOIN          |                |197     |1067        |
|8 |            ├─HASH JOIN        |                |485     |295         |
|9 |            │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|CUSTOMER_ADDRESS|500     |20          |
|10|            │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN|CUSTOMER        |1000    |52          |
|11|            └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |CATALOG_SALES   |4000    |284         |
===========================================================================
