|8 |        │ │ │ ├─SUBPLAN SCAN       |VIEW2   |10      |38          |
|9 |        │ │ │ │ └─HASH GROUP BY    |        |10      |38          |
|10|        │ │ │ │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN|J       |200     |13          |
|11|        │ │ │ └─HASH JOIN          |        |18      |474         |
|12|        │ │ │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |D       |30      |36          |
|13|        │ │ │   └─MERGE JOIN       |        |223     |411         |
|14|        │ │ │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|I       |200     |16          |
|15|        │ │ │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN|S       |5000    |340         |
|16|        │ │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET|C       |1       |16          |
|17|        │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |A       |500     |18          |
|18|        └─HASH DISTINCT            |        |18      |56          |
|19|          └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |DATE_DIM|30      |48          |
=======================================================================
